animeTitle: Oishinbo: Kyuukyoku tai Shikou, Chouju Ryouri Taiketsu!!
animeDescription: Ultimate Menu and Supreme Menu square off in a cooking battle about dishes that promote longevity. For Supreme's Kaibara Yuzan and Ultimate's Yamaoka Shirou (who are father and son), this confrontation is more than strictly business: it's personal.(Source: BakaBT)
